{"tid":784270,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"CR個新challenge準備15勝時俾人亂入玩輸左","createTime":"2018-08-18T08:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T09:27:55.000Z","uid":108894,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2baa639a2042f98e0532fc66d670b6ae5ca8e08b","tid":784270,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T08:43:52.000Z","msg":"今期有個新嘅2v2 challenge，靠住clan班大佬+朋友直取14勝<br />\n去到last一場準備再同個大佬夾多次贏埋佢<br />\n點解有條on9衝撚左入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時已經知佢廢柴一條，佢一入已經心諗未打完輸<br />\n當然亦不出我所料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為之前已輸2場我亦都無仇報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我即刻屌到佢開花，佢仲想企圖call馬叫D大佬踢我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩我同D大佬夠friend，佢地唔撚睬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老老實實如果係同埋大佬夾輸左，我最多哦兩句就再con game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但條友我明知佢廢根本唔預佢一齊打，佢又偏偏亂入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n贏左都算，輸左我真係好難唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644ed7ba6e73ac002307b962e3125ba1a114683f","tid":784270,"uid":156592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T08:51:03.000Z","msg":"咩公會？"},{"pid":"7a2a5011cfef7cfd73338f0a3ebbffa55